0430","n20431"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%B7%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to give power"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to illuminate"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to set out upon, to pull out upon, to draw upon","tags":["ditransitive"],"examples":[{"text":"وَٱلْآنَ، وَبِفَضْلِ سِيرَةٍ حَيَاتِيَّةٍ جَدِيدَةٍ، أَصْبَحَ بِٱسْتِطَاعَتِنَا أَنْ نَرَى جَانِبًا آخَرَ مِنْ جَوَانِبَ شَخْصِيَّةٍ جوزيف غوبلز وَهِيَ ٱلسِّيرَةُ ٱلَّتِي لَا تَكْشِفُ فَقَطْ كَيْفَ كَانَ مَهْوُوسًا بِهتلر إِلَى دَرَجَةِ ٱلْجُنُونِ، وَلٰكِنَّهَا تَتَنَاوَلُ أَيْضًا لِلْمَرَّةِ ٱلْأُولَى تَفَاصِيلَ حَيَاتِهِ ٱلشَّخْصِيَّةِ ٱلْمُنْحَرِفَةِ كَمَا أَنَّهَا تُسَلِّطُ ٱلضَّوْءَ عَلَى دَوْرِهِ غَيْرِ ٱلْمُتَوَقَّعِ كَـ«كازانوفا» وَكَـ«زِيرِ نِسَاءٍ» نازي.","english":"Now, thanks to a new biography, it has become possible for us to see an other side of the personality of Joseph Goebbels, and the biography does not only show how fanatical he was into Hitler up to the point of insanity, but it also treats for the first time the details of his perverted private life as it sheds light on his unexpected role as “Casanova” and Nazi “women visitor”."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of سُلْطَة (sulṭa)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n20427","headword_ar":"سَلُطَ","root":"slT","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"salaATapN","text_ar":"سَلَاطَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, B,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, overcame, prevailed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"predominated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, firm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"established, in superior power"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"force:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(B, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he possessed power of dominion"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sovereignty"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rule."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(anything, as, for instance, a solid hoof, and a camel's foot,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, strong,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hard."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, sharp."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And the same verb, (M, Msb, K,) inf. n. as above (S, M, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suluwTapN","text_ar":"سُلُوطَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, chaste,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perspicuous, in speech,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eloquent, and sharp in tongue:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"long-tongued;;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saliTa","text_ar":"سَلِطَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"salaTN","text_ar":"سَلَطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TS, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clamorous and foultongued:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) [or this verb, said of a man, has the first of these three significations; but]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saluTato","text_ar":"سَلُطَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"salaATapN","text_ar":"سَلَاطَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a woman)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, long-tongued, and vehemently clamorous."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth.) [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saliyTN","text_ar":"سَلِيطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below.]"}],"source_refs":["M","S","B","TA","Msb","K","TS"]},{"entry_id":"n20430","headword_ar":"سَلْطٌ","root":"slT","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saliyTN","text_ar":"سَلِيطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; for the former, in four places; and for the latter, in seven."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n20431","headword_ar":"سَلِطٌ","root":"slT","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saliyTN","text_ar":"سَلِيطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; for the former, in four places; and for the latter, in seven."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}